---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import depressedImage from '../assets/EmilyPhelan-Depressed.jpg';
import storyImage from '../assets/EmilyPhelan-London-YellowCard.jpg';
import feltLikeImage from '../assets/IMG_7228.jpg';
import differentHeadspaceImage from '../assets/EmilyPhelan-London-Playing-1.jpg';
import whyImage from '../assets/EmilyPhelan-Holloway-Playing.jpg';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';

const slides = [
  {
    image: storyImage,
    alt: 'Emily Phelan playing in London',
    kicker: 'Chapter 1',
    title: 'My Story',
    paragraphs: [
      'My name is Emily Phelan. I am a 32-year-old female athlete living in London, and I play Ladies Gaelic Football.',
      'Sport has always been a huge part of my life, but my journey with it has not been straightforward. I have struggled with anxiety and depression throughout my sporting career, and for a long time I did not have the language or the tools to understand what was happening in my own head.',
      'I did not understand why pressure felt like too much sometimes. I did not understand why my confidence could swing so much. I just knew I loved the sport, but I was also struggling in it.',
    ],
  },
  {
    image: depressedImage,
    alt: 'Emily Phelan on league final day',
    kicker: 'Chapter 2',
    title: 'A Difficult Phase',
    paragraphs: [
      'Number 18 is me on league final day. I remember feeling happy for my team, but I could not fully feel it for myself because I was so caught up in my own performance. I was not in a good place mentally, and that showed on the pitch.',
      'What I understand now, looking back, is that it was not just performance anxiety. I was dealing with undiagnosed anxiety and depression at the time, and that naturally spilled over into my sport.',
    ],
  },
  {
    image: feltLikeImage,
    alt: 'Emily Phelan during a game',
    kicker: 'Chapter 3',
    title: 'What That Felt Like',
    paragraphs: [
      'Everything felt heavier than it should have. Not just games, but life in general. There were days I struggled to get out of bed, times I felt really low for no clear reason, and panic attacks I did not fully understand at the time.',
      'My mind was constantly busy. I was overthinking, second-guessing myself, and never really fully present in the moment. Afterwards, I would replay everything in my head over and over, feeling disconnected from what had just happened.',
    ],
  },
  {
    image: differentHeadspaceImage,
    alt: 'Emily Phelan playing in London',
    kicker: 'Chapter 4',
    title: 'Hitting Rock Bottom',
    paragraphs: [
      'Eventually I hit rock bottom and went to my doctor. I was put on medication, and for the first time in years my head went quiet.',
      'That was when I realised how loud it had been. The overthinking had started when I was a teenager, and I had carried it for so long that I thought it was normal. I just did not know.',
      'Getting the right help was the turning point. It gave me space to think clearly, and from there I could finally start doing the work on the mental side of my sport and my life.',
    ],
  },
  {
    image: whyImage,
    alt: 'Emily Phelan playing for Holloway',
    kicker: 'Chapter 5',
    title: 'Why This Platform Exists',
    paragraphs: [
      'None of that happened overnight. It took a lot of work, a lot of learning, and a lot of uncomfortable reflection on how I was thinking, feeling, and showing up in life and in sport.',
      'Mind the Gael is the platform I wish I had when I was younger. The language, the tools, and the honest stories that would have helped me understand my own head much sooner.',
    ],
  },
];
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={`About | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="My Story - Emily Phelan's journey through anxiety, depression, and finding mental performance tools for sport." />
  </head>
  <body class="about-page">
    <Header />
    <main class="about-layout">
      <section class="about-intro">
        <h1>My Story</h1>
        <p class="about-intro-sub">Use the arrows or dots below to move through.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="slideshow" aria-roledescription="carousel" aria-label="Emily's story">
        <div class="slideshow-stage">
          {slides.map((slide, index) => (
            <article
              class:list={["slide", { active: index === 0 }]}
              data-slide-index={index}
              aria-roledescription="slide"
              aria-label={`${index + 1} of ${slides.length}: ${slide.title}`}
              aria-hidden={index !== 0 ? "true" : "false"}
            >
              <div class="slide-image-wrap">
                <Image
                  src={slide.image}
                  alt={slide.alt}
                  class="slide-image"
                  loading={index === 0 ? "eager" : "lazy"}
                  widths={[600, 900, 1200, 1600]}
                  sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 50vw"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="slide-copy">
                <p class="slide-kicker">{slide.kicker}</p>
                <h2>{slide.title}</h2>
                {slide.paragraphs.map((p) => <p>{p}</p>)}
              </div>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>

        <button type="button" class="slide-arrow slide-arrow-prev" id="slide-prev" aria-label="Previous chapter">
          <span aria-hidden="true">‹</span>
        </button>
        <button type="button" class="slide-arrow slide-arrow-next" id="slide-next" aria-label="Next chapter">
          <span aria-hidden="true">›</span>
        </button>

        <div class="slide-dots" role="tablist" aria-label="Choose a chapter">
          {slides.map((slide, index) => (
            <button
              type="button"
              class:list={["slide-dot", { active: index === 0 }]}
              data-target={index}
              role="tab"
              aria-label={`Go to ${slide.title}`}
              aria-selected={index === 0 ? "true" : "false"}
            ></button>
          ))}
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <Footer />

    <script is:inline>
      (() => {
        const stage = document.querySelector('.slideshow-stage');
        if (!stage) return;
        const slides = Array.from(stage.querySelectorAll('.slide'));
        const dots = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('.slide-dot'));
        const prevBtn = document.getElementById('slide-prev');
        const nextBtn = document.getElementById('slide-next');
        let current = 0;
        const total = slides.length;

        const goTo = (next) => {
          const target = ((next % total) + total) % total;
          if (target === current) return;
          slides[current].classList.remove('active');
          slides[current].setAttribute('aria-hidden', 'true');
          dots[current]?.classList.remove('active');
          dots[current]?.setAttribute('aria-selected', 'false');

          slides[target].classList.add('active');
          slides[target].setAttribute('aria-hidden', 'false');
          dots[target]?.classList.add('active');
          dots[target]?.setAttribute('aria-selected', 'true');
          current = target;
        };

        prevBtn?.addEventListener('click', () => goTo(current - 1));
        nextBtn?.addEventListener('click', () => goTo(current + 1));
        dots.forEach((dot, index) => {
          dot.addEventListener('click', () => goTo(index));
        });

        document.addEventListener('keydown', (event) => {
          if (event.key === 'ArrowLeft') goTo(current - 1);
          else if (event.key === 'ArrowRight') goTo(current + 1);
        });
      })();
    </script>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  .about-layout {
    padding: 0;
    background: var(--green-dark);
    min-height: calc(100vh - 220px);
  }

  /* ── Intro ── */
  .about-intro {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem 1.5rem;
    color: var(--green-light);
  }

  .about-intro-kicker {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--purple);
    margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
  }

  .about-intro h1 {
    margin: 0 0 0.7rem;
    color: var(--green-lime);
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .about-intro-sub {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--green-light);
    opacity: 0.78;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  /* ── Slideshow shell ── */
  .slideshow {
    position: relative;
    padding: 1.5rem 4.5rem 3.5rem;
    max-width: 880px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .slideshow-stage {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 620px;
  }

  /* ── Individual slide card ── */
  .slide {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid rgba(105, 0, 90, 0.18);
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: opacity 0.45s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 18px 38px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
  }

  .slide.active {
    opacity: 1;
    pointer-events: auto;
    position: relative;
    inset: auto;
  }

  .slide-image-wrap {
    width: 100%;
    background: #ffffff;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 1.5rem 1rem 0.5rem;
  }

  .slide-image {
    width: auto;
    max-width: 360px;
    max-height: 320px;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
    display: block;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .slide-copy {
    padding: 1.6rem 2rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .slide-kicker {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--purple);
    margin: 0 0 0.7rem;
  }

  .slide-copy h2 {
    margin: 0 0 1.1rem;
    color: var(--purple);
    font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 3vw, 2.3rem);
    line-height: 1.2;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .slide-copy p {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .slide-copy p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* ── Arrows: sit just outside the card on either side ── */
  .slide-arrow {
    position: absolute;
    top: calc(50% - 30px);
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--green-lime);
    color: var(--green-dark);
    border: none;
    font-size: 1.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
    cursor: pointer;
    z-index: 5;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
    transition: transform 0.18s ease, background 0.18s ease;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .slide-arrow:hover {
    background: var(--purple-light);
    transform: scale(1.08);
  }

  .slide-arrow-prev {
    left: 0.25rem;
  }

  .slide-arrow-next {
    right: 0.25rem;
  }

  /* ── Dots ── */
  .slide-dots {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    margin: 1.4rem 0 0;
  }

  .slide-dot {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: transparent;
    border: 2px solid var(--green-lime);
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0;
    transition: background 0.18s ease, transform 0.18s ease;
  }

  .slide-dot:hover {
    transform: scale(1.18);
  }

  .slide-dot.active {
    background: var(--green-lime);
  }

  /* ── Responsive ── */
  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .slideshow {
      padding: 1rem 1rem 3rem;
    }

    .slideshow-stage {
      min-height: 0;
    }

    .slide:not(.active) {
      display: none;
    }

    .slide-image {
      max-width: 100%;
      max-height: 240px;
    }

    .slide-copy {
      padding: 1.4rem 1.2rem 1.8rem;
    }

    .slide-arrow {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      top: calc(50% - 20px);
    }

    .slide-arrow-prev {
      left: -0.25rem;
    }

    .slide-arrow-next {
      right: -0.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
